data.name: Label3.Text
data.value:
I wanted to take this time to say well, Thanks! You all chipped into the development and even offered me hosting. To these people I say, Thanks! From the bottom of my heart.
You made this version possible, and as requested I'll post their names below here.

data.name: Label8.Text
data.value: I've decided to open the doors to the donations, with the more donations I get I can assure better content, servers, and more patches. I'll assemble a team and turn this into a propper developed tool, for you all to use. Our tool will also be free forever.
